    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="exercise-11.1---5563-reverse-game">Exercise 11.1 - 5563: ReverseGame</h1><h2 id="一.-题目大意">一. 题目大意</h2><p>给定 <span class="math inline"><em>T</em> ≤ 15</span> 组输入。</p><p>对于一个长宽为 <span class="math inline"><em>N</em> ≤ 200</span>的正方矩形。</p><p>进行 <span class="math inline"><em>Q</em> ≤ 2<em>e</em>4</span>次查询</p><p>每次修改反转 <strong>某个点</strong> 或者<strong>某一列</strong>。</p><p>要求每次修改后的 <strong>0</strong> 和 <strong>1</strong>连通块的数目。</p><h3 id="暴力解法-oqn2">1. 暴力解法 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>Q</em><em>N</em><sup>2</sup>)</span></h3><p>对于每个查询</p><p>修改：花费 <span class="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>N</em>)</span>(反转列) 或 <span class="math inline"><em>O</em>(1)</span> (反转点)的时间更新 <span class="math inline"><em>N</em> × <em>N</em></span> 的<spanclass="math inline"><em>g</em><em>r</em><em>i</em><em>d</em></span>数组。</p><p>查询：遍历整张表 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>N</em><sup>2</sup>)</span>查询连通块数量。</p><p>复杂度：每次查询都是 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>N</em><sup>2</sup> ⋅ <em>α</em>(<em>N</em><sup>2</sup>))</span>，近似<spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>N</em><sup>2</sup>)</span>。总复杂度<spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>Q</em> ⋅ <em>N</em><sup>2</sup>)</span>。</p><p>结论：这个复杂度太高了，导致 <spanclass="math inline"><em>T</em><em>L</em><em>E</em></span>了。o(╥﹏╥)o</p><h3 id="尝试优化中">2. 尝试优化中</h3><h4 id="初步构思中">2.1. 初步构思中</h4><p>问题：每次重新查询连通块数时，都需要 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>N</em><sup>2</sup>)</span>的开销，而我们只对一个点（1），或者一列（N）个值进行了修改。</p><p>观察发现：每次修改都可以算是对列的修改，不涉及行之间的修改。</p><p>不妨接着想，是否可以使用一个 <strong>维护区间信息</strong>的数据结构，来避免每次查询的 <spanclass="math inline"><em>O</em>(<em>N</em><sup>2</sup>)</span> 开销。</p><p>似乎：<strong>线段树</strong>是一个不错的选择，可以动态维护区间信息。 (๑´ڡ`๑)</p><h4 id="线段树">2.2. 线段树？</h4><p>通过上面的分析得出，因为修改只与列相关，所以我们可以在<strong>列</strong> 上建立线段树。</p><p>具体想法：线段树的区间 <spanclass="math inline">[<em>l</em>, <em>r</em>]</span> 可以存储 <spanclass="math inline">[<em>l</em>, 1]</span> 到 <spanclass="math inline">[<em>r</em>, <em>N</em>]</span> 之间的信息。</p><p>那么问题来了？每个区间应该维护什么信息？才能支持 <code>push_up</code>运算。</p><p>不难想到：存储连通块 <code>W[t]</code> 与 <code>B[t]</code>的数量。但是这样存储会有一个问题，在 <strong>区间合并</strong> 时，<spanclass="math inline"><em>W</em>[<em>l</em>] + <em>W</em>[<em>r</em>] ≠ <em>W</em>[<em>l</em> + <em>r</em>]</span>，若<code>mid</code> 与 <code>mid+1</code> 连通时，就会导致数量减少。</p><p>由于线段树存储的信息需要满足<strong>可合并性</strong>，因此我们还需要知道<strong>边界上的连通性</strong> 。 ( ´•̥̥̥ω•̥̥̥` )</p><h4 id="线段树的节点状态">2.3. 线段树的节点状态</h4><p>为了维护 <strong>边界上的连通性</strong>我们需要存储每个位置的信息。</p><p>因此不难想到：我们需要存储以下信息。</p><ul><li><code>W[t]</code>, <code>B[t]</code>即在不考虑边界情况下，黑白连通块数目。</li><li><code>lnum[i]</code> 表示第 <spanclass="math inline"><em>i</em></span> 行，第 <spanclass="math inline"><em>t</em></span> 列所处的连通块编号。</li><li><code>rnum[i]</code> 表示第 <spanclass="math inline"><em>i</em></span> 行，第 <spanclass="math inline"><em>t</em></span> 列所处的连通块编号。</li></ul><p>不难想到：为了维护最后两个 <code>lnum,rnum</code>，我们可以用并查集来优化查询。</p><h4 id="线段树的实现">2.4. 线段树的实现</h4><p>值得注意的一点是，并查集在每次查询修改后都需要重置</p><p>不然会被之前的数据污染！！！ o(╥﹏╥)o</p><h3 id="代码实现">3. 代码实现</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br><span class="line">96</span><br><span class="line">97</span><br><span class="line">98</span><br><span class="line">99</span><br><span class="line">100</span><br><span class="line">101</span><br><span class="line">102</span><br><span class="line">103</span><br><span class="line">104</span><br><span class="line">105</span><br><span class="line">106</span><br><span class="line">107</span><br><span class="line">108</span><br><span class="line">109</span><br><span class="line">110</span><br><span class="line">111</span><br><span class="line">112</span><br><span class="line">113</span><br><span class="line">114</span><br><span class="line">115</span><br><span class="line">116</span><br><span class="line">117</span><br><span class="line">118</span><br><span class="line">119</span><br><span class="line">120</span><br><span class="line">121</span><br><span class="line">122</span><br><span class="line">123</span><br><span class="line">124</span><br><span class="line">125</span><br><span class="line">126</span><br><span class="line">127</span><br><span class="line">128</span><br><span class="line">129</span><br><span class="line">130</span><br><span class="line">131</span><br><span class="line">132</span><br><span class="line">133</span><br><span class="line">134</span><br><span class="line">135</span><br><span class="line">136</span><br><span class="line">137</span><br><span class="line">138</span><br><span class="line">139</span><br><span class="line">140</span><br><span class="line">141</span><br><span class="line">142</span><br><span class="line">143</span><br><span class="line">144</span><br><span class="line">145</span><br><span class="line">146</span><br><span class="line">147</span><br><span class="line">148</span><br><span class="line">149</span><br><span class="line">150</span><br><span class="line">151</span><br><span class="line">152</span><br><span class="line">153</span><br><span class="line">154</span><br><span class="line">155</span><br><span class="line">156</span><br><span class="line">157</span><br><span class="line">158</span><br><span class="line">159</span><br><span class="line">160</span><br><span class="line">161</span><br><span class="line">162</span><br><span class="line">163</span><br><span class="line">164</span><br><span class="line">165</span><br><span class="line">166</span><br><span class="line">167</span><br><span class="line">168</span><br><span class="line">169</span><br><span class="line">170</span><br><span class="line">171</span><br><span class="line">172</span><br><span class="line">173</span><br><span class="line">174</span><br><span class="line">175</span><br><span class="line">176</span><br><span class="line">177</span><br><span class="line">178</span><br><span class="line">179</span><br><span class="line">180</span><br><span class="line">181</span><br><span class="line">182</span><br><span class="line">183</span><br><span class="line">184</span><br><span class="line">185</span><br><span class="line">186</span><br><span class="line">187</span><br><span class="line">188</span><br><span class="line">189</span><br><span class="line">190</span><br><span class="line">191</span><br><span class="line">192</span><br><span class="line">193</span><br><span class="line">194</span><br><span class="line">195</span><br><span class="line">196</span><br><span class="line">197</span><br><span class="line">198</span><br><span class="line">199</span><br><span class="line">200</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> maxn = <span class="hljs-number">200</span> + <span class="hljs-number">10</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">struct</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Node</span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> l, r;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> w, b;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> lnum[maxn];<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> rnum[maxn];<br>&#125;tree[maxn &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">2</span>];<br><br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> n, q;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> G[maxn][maxn];<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> fa[maxn * maxn];<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">getid</span><span class="hljs-params">( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> x, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> y )</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> x * n + y;<br>&#125;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 把二维数据转化为一维数据查询</span><br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">find</span><span class="hljs-params">( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> x )</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> x == fa[x] ? x : fa[x] = <span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>( fa[x] );<br>&#125;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 并查集</span><br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">init</span><span class="hljs-params">( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> u, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> col )</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 初始化叶子结点</span><br>    tree[u].b = tree[u].w = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i )<br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> id = <span class="hljs-built_in">getid</span>( i, col );<br>        fa[id] = id;<br>        tree[u].lnum[i] = id;<br>        tree[u].rnum[i] = id;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( G[i][col] == <span class="hljs-number">0</span> ) tree[u].w ++;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( G[i][col] == <span class="hljs-number">1</span> ) tree[u].b ++;<br>    &#125;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 初始化 w, b 的数目</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">2</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i )<br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( G[i][col] == G[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>][col] )<br>        &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> id = <span class="hljs-built_in">getid</span>( i, col );<br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> root = <span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>( <span class="hljs-built_in">getid</span>( i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>, col ) );<br><br>            fa[id] = root;<br>            tree[u].lnum[i] = root;<br>            tree[u].rnum[i] = root;<br>            <br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( G[i][col] == <span class="hljs-number">0</span> ) tree[u].w --;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( G[i][col] == <span class="hljs-number">1</span> ) tree[u].b --;            <br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 搜寻垂直的连通块数目</span><br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">push_up</span><span class="hljs-params">( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> u )</span> </span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 合并</span><br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> lson = u &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> rson = u &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span> | <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i )<br>    &#123;   <span class="hljs-comment">// ！！！很重要，因为每次查询后并查集数据都会乱</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 所以这里采用 push_up 中修改来代替每次查询重置并查集</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 因为我们每次查询只关心这些被修改的点</span><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 所以其他点的 fa 不用管</span><br>        fa[ tree[lson].lnum[i] ] = tree[lson].lnum[i];<br>        fa[ tree[lson].rnum[i] ] = tree[lson].rnum[i];<br>        fa[ tree[rson].lnum[i] ] = tree[rson].lnum[i];<br>        fa[ tree[rson].rnum[i] ] = tree[rson].rnum[i];<br>    &#125;<br><br>    tree[u].w = tree[lson].w + tree[rson].w;<br>    tree[u].b = tree[lson].b + tree[rson].b;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">//  左右连通块数目合并（暂时不考虑相连）</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> m = (tree[u].l + tree[u].r) &gt;&gt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">//  m 为 [l,r] 区间中的分割点</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i )<br>    &#123;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 计算左右相连的连通块，并减去这部分重复的</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( G[i][m] == G[i][m<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>] )<br>        &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> fx = <span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>( tree[lson].rnum[i] );<br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> fy = <span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>( tree[rson].lnum[i] );<br><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( fx != fy )<br>            &#123;<br>                fa[fx] = fy;<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( G[i][m] == <span class="hljs-number">0</span> ) tree[u].w --;<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( G[i][m] == <span class="hljs-number">1</span> ) tree[u].b --;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125; <br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 计算完相连部分后，重新更新左右边界</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 父节点的左边界 = 左子节点左边界的 &quot;新根&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 父节点的右边界 = 右子节点右边界的 &quot;新根&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i )<br>    &#123;<br>        tree[u].lnum[i] = <span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>( tree[lson].lnum[i] );<br>        tree[u].rnum[i] = <span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>( tree[rson].rnum[i] );<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ;    <br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">build</span><span class="hljs-params">( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> l, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> r, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> u )</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 递归建树</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 正常线段树逻辑</span><br>    tree[u].l = l;<br>    tree[u].r = r;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( l == r )<br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">init</span>( u, l );<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> m = ( l + r ) &gt;&gt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">build</span>( l, m, u &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span> );<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">build</span>( m<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>, r, u &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span> | <span class="hljs-number">1</span> );<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">push_up</span>( u );<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">update</span><span class="hljs-params">( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> c, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> l, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> r, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> u )</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 单点修改</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 正常线段树逻辑</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 因为我们把线段树压扁了</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 所以对于每列的修改同样只要修改一点即可</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( l == r )<br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">init</span>( u, c );<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> m = ( l + r ) &gt;&gt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( c &lt;= m ) <span class="hljs-built_in">update</span>( c, l, m, u &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span> );<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">update</span>( c, m<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>, r, u &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span> | <span class="hljs-number">1</span> );<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">push_up</span>( u );<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">solve</span><span class="hljs-params">( )</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; n;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i )<br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> j = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; j &lt;= n; ++ j ) <br>        &#123;<br>            cin &gt;&gt; G[i][j];<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">build</span>( <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, n, <span class="hljs-number">1</span> );<br><br>    cin &gt;&gt; q;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= q; ++ i )<br>    &#123;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> opt, x, y;<br>        cin &gt;&gt; opt;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( opt == <span class="hljs-number">1</span> )<br>        &#123;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 单点修改</span><br>            cin &gt;&gt; x;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i )<br>                G[i][x] ^= <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>            <span class="hljs-built_in">update</span>( x, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, n, <span class="hljs-number">1</span> );<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span><br>        &#123;   <span class="hljs-comment">// 某列修改</span><br>            cin &gt;&gt; x &gt;&gt; y;<br>            G[x][y] ^= <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>            <span class="hljs-built_in">update</span>( y, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, n, <span class="hljs-number">1</span> );<br>        &#125;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-comment">// 最后别忘了 1 和 n 是相连的</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>( <span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++ i )<br>        &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( G[i][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] == G[i][n] )<br>            &#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-type">int</span> fx = <span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>( tree[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>].lnum[i] );<br>                <span class="hljs-type">int</span> fy = <span class="hljs-built_in">find</span>( tree[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>].rnum[i] );<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( fx != fy )<br>                &#123;<br>                    fa[fx] = fy;<br>                    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( G[i][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] == <span class="hljs-number">0</span> ) tree[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>].w --;<br>                    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>( G[i][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] == <span class="hljs-number">1</span> ) tree[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>].b --;<br>                &#125;   <br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-comment">//输出答案即可</span><br>        cout &lt;&lt; tree[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>].w &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot; &quot;</span> &lt;&lt; tree[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>].b &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ;<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> t;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; t;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>( t -- ) <br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">solve</span>( );<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="二.-结语">二. 结语</h2><p>这题的细节太多太多太多啦！！！！</p><p>建议没事别写，真不是给人写的。</p><p>不知道写着写着是人先疯还是代码先疯。</p><p>感谢你能看到最后，愿我们一同前行。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
